            "body": "<p>The problem is now solved. The solution was obvious. As i put the button on a custom <code>VerticalFieldManager<\/code>, in the <code>VerticalFieldManager<\/code>'s sublayout method i had to change the parameters in it to <code>Display.USE_ALL_WIDTH<\/code>. That fixed the problem Thanks for the help. <\/p>\n",
